H. W. Brands, author and Dickson 
Allen Anderson Centennial Professor of History at the University
of Texas in Austin, talks with Bloomberg's Lewis Lapham about 
his new book, ``American Colossus: The Triumph of Capitalism, 
1865-1900.''  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 17:15  -0- Oct/22/2010 12:22 GMT
 